  "text": "In the numerical solution of linear equations system the Krylov subspace method is one of the most important classes of projective type numerical methods [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] . The iterative algorithms that are applied to solve large scale linear systems are mostly the preconditioned Krylov subspace methods [CITATION_6] .",
